body:
I think the issue about offset is located in:
https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/ca3bc0f1c2f917cf6e7c49d58f5ec604a9af9367/tensorflow/core/kernels/eigen_attention.h#L84-L98

Created a PR #12829 to fix it with the following changes:
```
      if (normalized_) {
        // Un-normalize coordinates back to pixel space if normalized.
        x *= input_width;
        y *= input_height;
        if (centered_) {
          // Un-center if coordinates are centered on the image center.
          x /= 2.0f;
          y /= 2.0f;
          x += input_width / 2.0f;
          y += input_height / 2.0f;
          // Remove half of the glimpse window.
          x -= width_ / 2.0f;
          y -= height_ / 2.0f;
        }
      } else {
        if (centered_) {
          x += input_width / 2.0f;
          y += input_height / 2.0f;
        }
      }
```
